  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of acupuncture protocol involving in
      Weizhong (BL4) and Huantiao (GB30) points in treating ankylosing spondylitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
